3251 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
3252 inline std::array<unsigned int, VectorizedArrayType::size()>
3253 FEEvaluationBaseData<dim, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::get_cell_ids()
3254  const
3255 {
3256  Assert(this->matrix_info != nullptr, ExcNotInitialized());
3257 
3258  const unsigned int n_lanes = VectorizedArrayType::size();
3259  std::array<unsigned int, n_lanes> cells;
3260 
3261  // initialize array
3262  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < n_lanes; ++i)
3263  cells[i] = numbers::invalid_unsigned_int;
3264 
3265  if ((is_face == false) ||
3266  (is_face &&
3267  this->dof_access_index ==
3268  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell &&
3269  this->is_interior_face))
3270  {
3271  // cell or interior face face (element-centric loop)
3272  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < n_lanes; ++i)
3273  cells[i] = cell * n_lanes + i;
3274  }
3275  else if (is_face &&
3276  this->dof_access_index ==
3277  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell &&
3278  this->is_interior_face == false)
3279  {
3280  // exterior face (element-centric loop): for this case, we need to
3281  // look into the FaceInfo field that collects information from both
3282  // sides of a face once for the global mesh, and pick the face id that
3283  // is not the local one (cell_this).
3284  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < n_lanes; i++)
3285  {
3286  // compute actual (non vectorized) cell ID
3287  const unsigned int cell_this = this->cell * n_lanes + i;
3288  // compute face ID
3289  unsigned int face_index =
3290  this->matrix_info->get_cell_and_face_to_plain_faces()(this->cell,
3291  this->face_no,
3292  i);
3293 
3294  if (face_index == numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
3295  continue; // invalid face ID: no neighbor on boundary
3296 
3297  // get cell ID on both sides of face
3298  auto cell_m = this->matrix_info->get_face_info(face_index / n_lanes)
3299  .cells_interior[face_index % n_lanes];
3300  auto cell_p = this->matrix_info->get_face_info(face_index / n_lanes)
3301  .cells_exterior[face_index % n_lanes];
3302 
3303  // compare the IDs with the given cell ID
3304  if (cell_m == cell_this)
3305  cells[i] = cell_p; // neighbor has the other ID
3306  else if (cell_p == cell_this)
3307  cells[i] = cell_m;
3308  }
3309  }
3310  else if (is_face)
3311  {
3312  // face-centric faces
3313  const unsigned int *cells_ =
3314  is_interior_face ?
3315  &this->matrix_info->get_face_info(cell).cells_interior[0] :
3316  &this->matrix_info->get_face_info(cell).cells_exterior[0];
3317  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < VectorizedArrayType::size(); ++i)
3318  if (cells_[i] != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
3319  cells[i] = cells_[i];
3320  }
3321 
3322  return cells;
3323 }

3396  auto cell_p = this->matrix_info->get_face_info(fn / v_len)
3397  .cells_exterior[fn % v_len];

3400  if (cell_m == cell_this)

3402  else if (cell_p == cell_this)
3403  cells[i] = cell_m;

3406  else

3747 
3748  const unsigned int tensor_dofs_per_component =
3749  Utilities::fixed_power<dim>(this->data->data.front().fe_degree + 1);
3750  const unsigned int dofs_per_component =
3751  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
3752  const unsigned int n_quadrature_points = this->n_quadrature_points;
3753

3755  std::max(tensor_dofs_per_component + 1, dofs_per_component) *
3756  n_components_ * 3 +
3757  2 * n_quadrature_points;

3759  shift + n_components_ * dofs_per_component +
3760  (n_components_ * ((dim * (dim + 1)) / 2 + dim + 1) * n_quadrature_points);
3761  this->scratch_data_array->resize_fast(allocated_size);
3762

3764  for (unsigned int c = 0; c < n_components_; ++c)
3765  {
3766  values_dofs[c] =
3767  this->scratch_data_array->begin() + c * dofs_per_component;
3768  }
3769  values_quad =
3770  this->scratch_data_array->begin() + n_components * dofs_per_component;

3772  n_components * (dofs_per_component + n_quadrature_points);
3773  hessians_quad =
3774  this->scratch_data_array->begin() +
3775  n_components * (dofs_per_component + (dim + 1) * n_quadrature_points);
3776  this->scratch_data =
3777  this->scratch_data_array->begin() + n_components_ * dofs_per_component +

3802  }

3807  {
3808  using BaseVectorType = VectorType;
3809 
3810  static BaseVectorType *
3811  get_vector_component(VectorType &vec, const unsigned int component)
3812  {
3813  // FEEvaluation allows to combine several vectors from a scalar
3814  // FiniteElement into a "vector-valued" FEEvaluation object with
3815  // multiple components. These components can be extracted with the other
3816  // get_vector_component functions. If we do not get a vector of vectors
3817  // (std::vector<VectorType>, std::vector<VectorType*>, BlockVector), we

3820  // only get the zeroth component in the vector contained set nullptr for
3821  // the others which allows us to catch unintended use in
3822  // read_write_operation.
3823  if (component == 0)
3824  return &vec;
3825  else
3826  return nullptr;
3827  }
3828  };

3862  int n_components_,
3863  typename Number,

3865  typename VectorizedArrayType>

3867 inline void
3868 FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
3869  read_write_operation(
3870  const VectorOperation & operation,
3871  const std::array<VectorType *, n_components_> &src,
3872  const std::array<
3873  const std::vector<ArrayView<const typename VectorType::value_type>> *,
3874  n_components_> & src_sm,
3875  const std::bitset<VectorizedArrayType::size()> &mask,
3876  const bool apply_constraints) const
3877 {
3878  // Case 1: No MatrixFree object given, simple case because we do not need to
3879  // process constraints and need not care about vectorization -> go to
3880  // separate function
3881  if (this->matrix_info == nullptr)
3882  {
3883  read_write_operation_global(operation, src);
3884  return;
3885  }
3886 
3887  Assert(this->dof_info != nullptr, ExcNotInitialized());
3888  Assert(this->matrix_info->indices_initialized() == true, ExcNotInitialized());
3889  if (n_fe_components == 1)
3890  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
3891  {
3892  Assert(src[comp] != nullptr,
3893  ExcMessage("The finite element underlying this FEEvaluation "
3894  "object is scalar, but you requested " +
3895  std::to_string(n_components) +
3896  " components via the template argument in "
3897  "FEEvaluation. In that case, you must pass an "
3898  "std::vector<VectorType> or a BlockVector to " +
3899  "read_dof_values and distribute_local_to_global."));
3900  internal::check_vector_compatibility(*src[comp], *this->dof_info);
3901  }
3902  else
3903  {
3904  internal::check_vector_compatibility(*src[0], *this->dof_info);
3905  }
3906 
3907  // Case 2: contiguous indices which use reduced storage of indices and can
3908  // use vectorized load/store operations -> go to separate function
3909  AssertIndexRange(
3910  this->cell,
3911  this->dof_info->index_storage_variants[this->dof_access_index].size());
3912  if (this->dof_info->index_storage_variants
3913  [is_face ? this->dof_access_index :
3914  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell]
3915  [this->cell] >=
3916  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::contiguous)
3917  {
3918  read_write_operation_contiguous(operation, src, src_sm, mask);
3919  return;
3920  }
3921 
3922  // Case 3: standard operation with one index per degree of freedom -> go on
3923  // here
3924  constexpr unsigned int n_lanes = VectorizedArrayType::size();
3925  Assert(mask.count() == n_lanes,
3926  ExcNotImplemented("Masking currently not implemented for "
3927  "non-contiguous DoF storage"));
3928 
3929  std::integral_constant<bool,
3930  internal::is_vectorizable<VectorType, Number>::value>
3931  vector_selector;
3932 
3933  const unsigned int dofs_per_component =
3934  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
3935  if (this->dof_info->index_storage_variants
3936  [is_face ? this->dof_access_index :
3937  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell]
3938  [this->cell] ==
3939  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::interleaved)
3940  {
3941  const unsigned int *dof_indices =
3942  this->dof_info->dof_indices_interleaved.data() +
3943  this->dof_info->row_starts[this->cell * n_fe_components * n_lanes]
3944  .first +
3945  this->dof_info
3946  ->component_dof_indices_offset[this->active_fe_index]
3947  [this->first_selected_component] *
3948  n_lanes;
3949  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
3950  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dofs_per_component;
3951  ++i, dof_indices += n_lanes)
3952  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
3953  operation.process_dof_gather(dof_indices,
3954  *src[comp],
3955  0,
3956  values_dofs[comp][i],
3957  vector_selector);
3958  else
3959  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
3960  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dofs_per_component;
3961  ++i, dof_indices += n_lanes)
3962  operation.process_dof_gather(
3963  dof_indices, *src[0], 0, values_dofs[comp][i], vector_selector);
3964  return;
3965  }
3966 
3967  const unsigned int * dof_indices[n_lanes];
3968  VectorizedArrayType **values_dofs =
3969  const_cast<VectorizedArrayType **>(&this->values_dofs[0]);
3970 
3971  // Assign the appropriate cell ids for face/cell case and get the pointers
3972  // to the dof indices of the cells on all lanes
3973  unsigned int cells_copied[n_lanes];
3974  const unsigned int *cells;
3975  unsigned int n_vectorization_actual =
3976  this->dof_info
3977  ->n_vectorization_lanes_filled[this->dof_access_index][this->cell];
3978  bool has_constraints = false;
3979  const unsigned int n_components_read = n_fe_components > 1 ? n_components : 1;
3980  if (is_face)
3981  {
3982  if (this->dof_access_index ==
3983  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell)
3984  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_vectorization_actual; ++v)
3985  cells_copied[v] = this->cell * VectorizedArrayType::size() + v;
3986  cells =
3987  this->dof_access_index ==
3988  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell ?
3989  &cells_copied[0] :
3990  (this->is_interior_face ?
3991  &this->matrix_info->get_face_info(this->cell).cells_interior[0] :
3992  &this->matrix_info->get_face_info(this->cell).cells_exterior[0]);
3993  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_vectorization_actual; ++v)
3994  {
3995  Assert(cells[v] < this->dof_info->row_starts.size() - 1,
3996  ExcInternalError());
3997  const std::pair<unsigned int, unsigned int> *my_index_start =
3998  &this->dof_info->row_starts[cells[v] * n_fe_components +
3999  first_selected_component];
4000 
4001  // check whether any of the SIMD lanes has constraints, i.e., the
4002  // constraint indicator which is the second entry of row_starts
4003  // increments on this cell
4004  if (my_index_start[n_components_read].second !=
4005  my_index_start[0].second)
4006  has_constraints = true;
4007 
4008  dof_indices[v] =
4009  this->dof_info->dof_indices.data() + my_index_start[0].first;
4010  }
4011  for (unsigned int v = n_vectorization_actual; v < n_lanes; ++v)
4012  dof_indices[v] = nullptr;
4013  }
4014  else
4015  {
4016  AssertIndexRange((this->cell + 1) * n_lanes * n_fe_components,
4017  this->dof_info->row_starts.size());
4018  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_vectorization_actual; ++v)
4019  {
4020  const std::pair<unsigned int, unsigned int> *my_index_start =
4021  &this->dof_info
4022  ->row_starts[(this->cell * n_lanes + v) * n_fe_components +
4023  first_selected_component];
4024  if (my_index_start[n_components_read].second !=
4025  my_index_start[0].second)
4026  has_constraints = true;
4027  Assert(my_index_start[n_components_read].first ==
4028  my_index_start[0].first ||
4029  my_index_start[0].first < this->dof_info->dof_indices.size(),
4030  ExcIndexRange(0,
4031  my_index_start[0].first,
4032  this->dof_info->dof_indices.size()));
4033  dof_indices[v] =
4034  this->dof_info->dof_indices.data() + my_index_start[0].first;
4035  }
4036  for (unsigned int v = n_vectorization_actual; v < n_lanes; ++v)
4037  dof_indices[v] = nullptr;
4038  }
4039 
4040  // Case where we have no constraints throughout the whole cell: Can go
4041  // through the list of DoFs directly
4042  if (!has_constraints)
4043  {
4044  if (n_vectorization_actual < n_lanes)
4045  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4046  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dofs_per_component; ++i)
4047  operation.process_empty(values_dofs[comp][i]);
4048  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4049  {
4050  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_vectorization_actual; ++v)
4051  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dofs_per_component; ++i)
4052  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4053  operation.process_dof(dof_indices[v][i],
4054  *src[comp],
4055  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4056  }
4057  else
4058  {
4059  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4060  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_vectorization_actual; ++v)
4061  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dofs_per_component; ++i)
4062  operation.process_dof(
4063  dof_indices[v][comp * dofs_per_component + i],
4064  *src[0],
4065  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4066  }
4067  return;

4071  // all vector components that are filled and then over local dofs. ind_local
4072  // holds local number on cell, index iterates over the elements of
4073  // index_local_to_global and dof_indices points to the global indices stored
4074  // in index_local_to_global
4075  if (n_vectorization_actual < n_lanes)
4076  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4077  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dofs_per_component; ++i)
4078  operation.process_empty(values_dofs[comp][i]);

4082  is_face ? cells[v] : this->cell * n_lanes + v;
4083  const unsigned int cell_dof_index =
4084  cell_index * n_fe_components + first_selected_component;
4085  const unsigned int n_components_read =
4086  n_fe_components > 1 ? n_components : 1;

4088  this->dof_info->row_starts[cell_dof_index].second;
4089  unsigned int next_index_indicators =
4090  this->dof_info->row_starts[cell_dof_index + 1].second;
4091

4093  // unconstrained indices
4094  if (apply_constraints == false &&
4095  this->dof_info->row_starts[cell_dof_index].second !=
4096  this->dof_info->row_starts[cell_dof_index + n_components_read]
4097  .second)
4098  {
4099  Assert(this->dof_info->row_starts_plain_indices[cell_index] !=
4100  numbers::invalid_unsigned_int,
4101  ExcNotInitialized());

4103  this->dof_info->plain_dof_indices.data() +
4104  this->dof_info
4105  ->component_dof_indices_offset[this->active_fe_index]
4106  [this->first_selected_component] +

4119  for (unsigned int j = 0; j < indicator.first; ++j)

4129  // combination of the global value according to constraints
4130  Number value[n_components];
4131  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4132  operation.pre_constraints(values_dofs[comp][ind_local][v],

4136  this->matrix_info->constraint_pool_begin(indicator.second);

4138  this->matrix_info->constraint_pool_end(indicator.second);

4167  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4168  {

4172  for (; index_indicators != next_index_indicators;

4174  {

4182  values_dofs[comp][ind_local + j][v]);

4185

4188  Number value;
4189  operation.pre_constraints(values_dofs[comp][ind_local][v],
4190  value);
4191

4195  this->matrix_info->constraint_pool_end(indicator.second);

4213  {

4267 template <typename VectorType, typename VectorOperation>

4269 FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
4270  read_write_operation_contiguous(
4271  const VectorOperation & operation,
4272  const std::array<VectorType *, n_components_> &src,
4273  const std::array<
4274  const std::vector<ArrayView<const typename VectorType::value_type>> *,
4275  n_components_> & vectors_sm,
4276  const std::bitset<VectorizedArrayType::size()> &mask) const
4277 {
4278  // This functions processes the functions read_dof_values,
4279  // distribute_local_to_global, and set_dof_values with the same code for
4280  // contiguous cell indices (DG case). The distinction between these three
4281  // cases is made by the input VectorOperation that either reads values from
4282  // a vector and puts the data into the local data field or write local data
4283  // into the vector. Certain operations are no-ops for the given use case.
4284 
4285  std::integral_constant<bool,
4286  internal::is_vectorizable<VectorType, Number>::value>
4287  vector_selector;
4288  const internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::DoFAccessIndex ind =
4289  is_face ? this->dof_access_index :
4290  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell;
4291  const unsigned int n_lanes = mask.count();
4292 
4293  const std::vector<unsigned int> &dof_indices_cont =
4294  this->dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous[ind];
4295 
4296  // Simple case: We have contiguous storage, so we can simply copy out the
4297  // data
4298  if ((this->dof_info->index_storage_variants[ind][this->cell] ==
4299  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::
4300  interleaved_contiguous &&
4301  n_lanes == VectorizedArrayType::size()) &&
4302  !(is_face &&
4303  this->dof_access_index ==
4304  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell &&
4305  this->is_interior_face == false))
4306  {
4307  const unsigned int dof_index =
4308  dof_indices_cont[this->cell * VectorizedArrayType::size()] +
4309  this->dof_info->component_dof_indices_offset[this->active_fe_index]
4310  [first_selected_component] *
4311  VectorizedArrayType::size();
4312  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4313  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4314  operation.process_dofs_vectorized(
4315  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell,
4316  dof_index,
4317  *src[comp],
4318  values_dofs[comp],
4319  vector_selector);
4320  else
4321  operation.process_dofs_vectorized(
4322  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell * n_components,
4323  dof_index,
4324  *src[0],
4325  values_dofs[0],
4326  vector_selector);
4327  return;
4328  }
4329 
4330  std::array<unsigned int, VectorizedArrayType::size()> cells =
4331  this->get_cell_or_face_ids();
4332 
4333  // More general case: Must go through the components one by one and apply
4334  // some transformations
4335  const unsigned int n_filled_lanes =
4336  this->dof_info->n_vectorization_lanes_filled[ind][this->cell];
4337 
4338  const bool is_ecl =
4339  this->dof_access_index ==
4340  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell &&
4341  this->is_interior_face == false;
4342 
4343  if (vectors_sm[0] != nullptr)
4344  {
4345  const auto compute_vector_ptrs = [&](const unsigned int comp) {
4346  std::array<typename VectorType::value_type *,
4347  VectorizedArrayType::size()>
4348  vector_ptrs = {};
4349 
4350  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4351  {
4352  Assert(cells[v] != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int,
4353  ExcNotImplemented());
4354  Assert(ind < this->dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous_sm.size(),
4355  ExcIndexRange(
4356  ind, 0, this->dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous_sm.size()));
4357  Assert(cells[v] <
4358  this->dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous_sm[ind].size(),
4359  ExcIndexRange(
4360  cells[v],
4361  0,
4362  this->dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous_sm[ind].size()));
4363 
4364  const auto &temp =
4365  this->dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous_sm[ind][cells[v]];
4366 
4367  if (temp.first != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
4368  vector_ptrs[v] = const_cast<typename VectorType::value_type *>(
4369  vectors_sm[comp]->operator[](temp.first).data() + temp.second +
4370  this->dof_info->component_dof_indices_offset
4371  [this->active_fe_index][this->first_selected_component]);
4372  else
4373  vector_ptrs[v] = nullptr;
4374  }
4375  for (unsigned int v = n_filled_lanes; v < VectorizedArrayType::size();
4376  ++v)
4377  vector_ptrs[v] = nullptr;
4378 
4379  return vector_ptrs;
4380  };
4381 
4382  if (n_filled_lanes == VectorizedArrayType::size() &&
4383  n_lanes == VectorizedArrayType::size() && !is_ecl)
4384  {
4385  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4386  {
4387  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4388  {
4389  auto vector_ptrs = compute_vector_ptrs(comp);
4390  operation.process_dofs_vectorized_transpose(
4391  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell,
4392  vector_ptrs,
4393  values_dofs[comp],
4394  vector_selector);
4395  }
4396  }
4397  else
4398  {
4399  auto vector_ptrs = compute_vector_ptrs(0);
4400  operation.process_dofs_vectorized_transpose(
4401  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell * n_components,
4402  vector_ptrs,
4403  &values_dofs[0][0],
4404  vector_selector);
4405  }
4406  }
4407  else
4408  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4409  {
4410  auto vector_ptrs = compute_vector_ptrs(
4411  (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1) ? comp : 0);
4412 
4413  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4414  ++i)
4415  operation.process_empty(values_dofs[comp][i]);
4416 
4417  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4418  {
4419  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4420  if (mask[v] == true)
4421  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4422  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4423  ++i)
4424  operation.process_dof(vector_ptrs[v][i],
4425  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4426  }
4427  else
4428  {
4429  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4430  if (mask[v] == true)
4431  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4432  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4433  ++i)
4434  operation.process_dof(
4435  vector_ptrs[v]
4436  [i + comp * this->data
4437  ->dofs_per_component_on_cell],
4438  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4439  }
4440  }
4441  return;
4442  }
4443 
4444  unsigned int dof_indices[VectorizedArrayType::size()];
4445 
4446  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4447  {
4448  Assert(cells[v] != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int, ExcNotImplemented());
4449  dof_indices[v] =
4450  dof_indices_cont[cells[v]] +
4451  this->dof_info
4452  ->component_dof_indices_offset[this->active_fe_index]
4453  [this->first_selected_component] *
4454  this->dof_info->dof_indices_interleave_strides[ind][cells[v]];
4455  }
4456 
4457  for (unsigned int v = n_filled_lanes; v < VectorizedArrayType::size(); ++v)
4458  dof_indices[v] = numbers::invalid_unsigned_int;
4459 
4460  // In the case with contiguous cell indices, we know that there are no
4461  // constraints and that the indices within each element are contiguous
4462  if (n_filled_lanes == VectorizedArrayType::size() &&
4463  n_lanes == VectorizedArrayType::size() && !is_ecl)
4464  {
4465  if (this->dof_info->index_storage_variants[ind][this->cell] ==
4466  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::
4467  contiguous)
4468  {
4469  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4470  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4471  operation.process_dofs_vectorized_transpose(
4472  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell,
4473  dof_indices,
4474  *src[comp],
4475  values_dofs[comp],
4476  vector_selector);
4477  else
4478  operation.process_dofs_vectorized_transpose(
4479  this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell * n_components,
4480  dof_indices,
4481  *src[0],
4482  &values_dofs[0][0],
4483  vector_selector);
4484  }
4485  else if (this->dof_info->index_storage_variants[ind][this->cell] ==
4486  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::
4487  interleaved_contiguous_strided)
4488  {
4489  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4490  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4491  ++i)
4492  {
4493  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4494  operation.process_dof_gather(dof_indices,
4495  *src[comp],
4496  i * VectorizedArrayType::size(),
4497  values_dofs[comp][i],
4498  vector_selector);
4499  }
4500  else
4501  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4502  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4503  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4504  ++i)
4505  {
4506  operation.process_dof_gather(
4507  dof_indices,
4508  *src[0],
4509  (comp * this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell + i) *
4510  VectorizedArrayType::size(),
4511  values_dofs[comp][i],
4512  vector_selector);
4513  }
4514  }
4515  else
4516  {
4517  Assert(this->dof_info->index_storage_variants[ind][this->cell] ==
4518  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::
4519  IndexStorageVariants::interleaved_contiguous_mixed_strides,
4520  ExcNotImplemented());
4521  const unsigned int *offsets =
4522  &this->dof_info->dof_indices_interleave_strides
4523  [ind][VectorizedArrayType::size() * this->cell];
4524  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4525  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4526  ++i)
4527  {
4528  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4529  operation.process_dof_gather(dof_indices,
4530  *src[comp],
4531  0,
4532  values_dofs[comp][i],
4533  vector_selector);
4534  DEAL_II_OPENMP_SIMD_PRAGMA
4535  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < VectorizedArrayType::size(); ++v)
4536  dof_indices[v] += offsets[v];
4537  }
4538  else
4539  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4540  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4541  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4542  ++i)
4543  {
4544  operation.process_dof_gather(dof_indices,
4545  *src[0],
4546  0,
4547  values_dofs[comp][i],
4548  vector_selector);
4549  DEAL_II_OPENMP_SIMD_PRAGMA
4550  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < VectorizedArrayType::size(); ++v)
4551  dof_indices[v] += offsets[v];
4552  }
4553  }
4554  }
4555  else
4556  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
4557  {
4558  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4559  ++i)
4560  operation.process_empty(values_dofs[comp][i]);
4561  if (this->dof_info->index_storage_variants[ind][this->cell] ==
4562  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::
4563  contiguous)
4564  {
4565  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4566  {
4567  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4568  if (mask[v] == true)
4569  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4570  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4571  ++i)
4572  operation.process_dof(dof_indices[v] + i,
4573  *src[comp],
4574  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4575  }
4576  else
4577  {
4578  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4579  if (mask[v] == true)
4580  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4581  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4582  ++i)
4583  operation.process_dof(
4584  dof_indices[v] + i +
4585  comp * this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell,
4586  *src[0],
4587  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4588  }
4589  }
4590  else
4591  {
4592  const unsigned int *offsets =
4593  &this->dof_info->dof_indices_interleave_strides
4594  [ind][VectorizedArrayType::size() * this->cell];
4595  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4596  AssertIndexRange(offsets[v], VectorizedArrayType::size() + 1);
4597  if (n_components == 1 || n_fe_components == 1)
4598  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4599  {
4600  if (mask[v] == true)
4601  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4602  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4603  ++i)
4604  operation.process_dof(dof_indices[v] + i * offsets[v],
4605  *src[comp],
4606  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4607  }
4608  else
4609  {
4610  for (unsigned int v = 0; v < n_filled_lanes; ++v)
4611  if (mask[v] == true)
4612  for (unsigned int i = 0;
4613  i < this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell;
4614  ++i)
4615  operation.process_dof(
4616  dof_indices[v] +
4617  (i + comp * this->data->dofs_per_component_on_cell) *
4618  offsets[v],
4619  *src[0],
4620  values_dofs[comp][i][v]);
4621  }
4622  }
4623  }

5092  int n_components_,
5093  typename Number,
5094  bool is_face,
5095  typename VectorizedArrayType>
5096 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE
5097  Tensor<1, n_components_, Tensor<1, dim, VectorizedArrayType>>
5098  FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
5099  get_gradient(const unsigned int q_point) const
5100 {
5101 # ifdef DEBUG
5102  Assert(this->gradients_quad_initialized == true,
5103  internal::ExcAccessToUninitializedField());
5104 # endif
5105 
5106  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
5107  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
5108  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
5109  "update_gradients"));
5110  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
5111  Tensor<1, n_components_, Tensor<1, dim, VectorizedArrayType>> grad_out;
5112 
5113  // Cartesian cell
5114  if (!is_face && this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
5115  {
5116  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5117  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5118  grad_out[comp][d] = gradients_quad[(comp * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] *
5119  this->jacobian[0][d][d];
5120  }
5121  // cell with general/affine Jacobian
5122  else
5123  {
5124  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
5125  this->jacobian[this->cell_type > internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
5126  q_point :
5127  0];
5128  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5129  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5130  {
5131  grad_out[comp][d] =
5132  jac[d][0] * gradients_quad[(comp * dim) * nqp + q_point];
5133  for (unsigned int e = 1; e < dim; ++e)
5134  grad_out[comp][d] +=
5135  jac[d][e] * gradients_quad[(comp * dim + e) * nqp + q_point];
5136  }
5137  }
5138  return grad_out;

5187 namespace internal
5188 {
5189  // compute tmp = hess_unit(u) * J^T. do this manually because we do not
5190  // store the lower diagonal because of symmetry
5191  template <typename VectorizedArrayType>
5192  inline void
5193  hessian_unit_times_jac(const Tensor<2, 1, VectorizedArrayType> &jac,
5194  const VectorizedArrayType *const hessians,
5195  const unsigned int,
5196  VectorizedArrayType (&tmp)[1][1])
5197  {
5198  tmp[0][0] = jac[0][0] * hessians[0];
5199  }
5200 
5201  template <typename VectorizedArrayType>
5202  inline void
5203  hessian_unit_times_jac(const Tensor<2, 2, VectorizedArrayType> &jac,
5204  const VectorizedArrayType *const hessians,
5205  const unsigned int nqp,
5206  VectorizedArrayType (&tmp)[2][2])
5207  {
5208  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < 2; ++d)
5209  {
5210  tmp[0][d] = (jac[d][0] * hessians[0] + jac[d][1] * hessians[2 * nqp]);
5211  tmp[1][d] =
5212  (jac[d][0] * hessians[2 * nqp] + jac[d][1] * hessians[1 * nqp]);
5213  }
5214  }
5215 
5216  template <typename VectorizedArrayType>
5217  inline void
5218  hessian_unit_times_jac(const Tensor<2, 3, VectorizedArrayType> &jac,
5219  const VectorizedArrayType *const hessians,
5220  const unsigned int nqp,
5221  VectorizedArrayType (&tmp)[3][3])
5222  {
5223  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < 3; ++d)
5224  {
5225  tmp[0][d] =
5226  (jac[d][0] * hessians[0 * nqp] + jac[d][1] * hessians[3 * nqp] +
5227  jac[d][2] * hessians[4 * nqp]);
5228  tmp[1][d] =
5229  (jac[d][0] * hessians[3 * nqp] + jac[d][1] * hessians[1 * nqp] +
5230  jac[d][2] * hessians[5 * nqp]);
5231  tmp[2][d] =
5232  (jac[d][0] * hessians[4 * nqp] + jac[d][1] * hessians[5 * nqp] +
5233  jac[d][2] * hessians[2 * nqp]);
5234  }
5235  }
5236 } // namespace internal

5240 template <int dim,
5241  int n_components_,
5242  typename Number,
5243  bool is_face,
5244  typename VectorizedArrayType>
5245 inline Tensor<1, n_components_, Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType>>
5246 FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
5247  get_hessian(const unsigned int q_point) const
5248 {
5249  Assert(!is_face, ExcNotImplemented());
5250 # ifdef DEBUG
5251  Assert(this->hessians_quad_initialized == true,
5252  internal::ExcAccessToUninitializedField());
5253 # endif
5254  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
5255 
5256  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
5257  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
5258  "update_hessian"));
5259  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
5260  this->jacobian[this->cell_type <= internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
5261  0 :
5262  q_point];
5263 
5264  Tensor<1, n_components, Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType>> hessian_out;
5265 
5266  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
5267  constexpr unsigned int hdim = (dim * (dim + 1)) / 2;
5268 
5269  // Cartesian cell
5270  if (this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
5271  {
5272  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5273  {
5274  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5275  hessian_out[comp][d][d] =
5276  hessians_quad[(comp * hdim + d) * nqp + q_point] *
5277  (jac[d][d] * jac[d][d]);
5278  switch (dim)
5279  {
5280  case 1:
5281  break;
5282  case 2:
5283  hessian_out[comp][0][1] =
5284  hessians_quad[(comp * hdim + 2) * nqp + q_point] *
5285  (jac[0][0] * jac[1][1]);
5286  break;
5287  case 3:
5288  hessian_out[comp][0][1] =
5289  hessians_quad[(comp * hdim + 3) * nqp + q_point] *
5290  (jac[0][0] * jac[1][1]);
5291  hessian_out[comp][0][2] =
5292  hessians_quad[(comp * hdim + 4) * nqp + q_point] *
5293  (jac[0][0] * jac[2][2]);
5294  hessian_out[comp][1][2] =
5295  hessians_quad[(comp * hdim + 5) * nqp + q_point] *
5296  (jac[1][1] * jac[2][2]);
5297  break;
5298  default:
5299  Assert(false, ExcNotImplemented());
5300  }
5301  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5302  for (unsigned int e = d + 1; e < dim; ++e)
5303  hessian_out[comp][e][d] = hessian_out[comp][d][e];
5304  }
5305  }
5306  // cell with general Jacobian, but constant within the cell
5307  else if (this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine)
5308  {
5309  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5310  {
5311  VectorizedArrayType tmp[dim][dim];
5312  internal::hessian_unit_times_jac(
5313  jac, hessians_quad + comp * hdim * nqp + q_point, nqp, tmp);
5314 
5315  // compute first part of hessian, J * tmp = J * hess_unit(u) * J^T
5316  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5317  for (unsigned int e = d; e < dim; ++e)
5318  {
5319  hessian_out[comp][d][e] = jac[d][0] * tmp[0][e];
5320  for (unsigned int f = 1; f < dim; ++f)
5321  hessian_out[comp][d][e] += jac[d][f] * tmp[f][e];
5322  }
5323 
5324  // no J' * grad(u) part here because the Jacobian is constant
5325  // throughout the cell and hence, its derivative is zero
5326 
5327  // take symmetric part
5328  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5329  for (unsigned int e = d + 1; e < dim; ++e)
5330  hessian_out[comp][e][d] = hessian_out[comp][d][e];
5331  }
5332  }
5333  // cell with general Jacobian
5334  else
5335  {
5336  const auto &jac_grad =
5337  this->mapping_data->jacobian_gradients
5338  [1 - this->is_interior_face]
5339  [this->mapping_data->data_index_offsets[this->cell] + q_point];
5340  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5341  {
5342  // compute laplacian before the gradient because it needs to access
5343  // unscaled gradient data
5344  VectorizedArrayType tmp[dim][dim];
5345  internal::hessian_unit_times_jac(
5346  jac, hessians_quad + comp * hdim * nqp + q_point, nqp, tmp);
5347 
5348  // compute first part of hessian, J * tmp = J * hess_unit(u) * J^T
5349  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5350  for (unsigned int e = d; e < dim; ++e)
5351  {
5352  hessian_out[comp][d][e] = jac[d][0] * tmp[0][e];
5353  for (unsigned int f = 1; f < dim; ++f)
5354  hessian_out[comp][d][e] += jac[d][f] * tmp[f][e];
5355  }
5356 
5357  // add diagonal part of J' * grad(u)
5358  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5359  for (unsigned int e = 0; e < dim; ++e)
5360  hessian_out[comp][d][d] +=
5361  jac_grad[d][e] *
5362  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + e) * nqp + q_point];
5363 
5364  // add off-diagonal part of J' * grad(u)
5365  for (unsigned int d = 0, count = dim; d < dim; ++d)
5366  for (unsigned int e = d + 1; e < dim; ++e, ++count)
5367  for (unsigned int f = 0; f < dim; ++f)
5368  hessian_out[comp][d][e] +=
5369  jac_grad[count][f] *
5370  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + f) * nqp + q_point];
5371 
5372  // take symmetric part
5373  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5374  for (unsigned int e = d + 1; e < dim; ++e)
5375  hessian_out[comp][e][d] = hessian_out[comp][d][e];
5376  }
5377  }
5378  return hessian_out;
5379 }

5477  typename Number,
5478  bool is_face,
5479  typename VectorizedArrayType>
5480 inline Tensor<1, n_components_, VectorizedArrayType>
5481 FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
5482  get_laplacian(const unsigned int q_point) const
5483 {
5484  Assert(is_face == false, ExcNotImplemented());
5485 # ifdef DEBUG
5486  Assert(this->hessians_quad_initialized == true,
5487  internal::ExcAccessToUninitializedField());
5488 # endif
5489  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
5490 
5491  Tensor<1, n_components_, VectorizedArrayType> laplacian_out;
5492  const auto hess_diag = get_hessian_diagonal(q_point);
5493  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
5494  {
5495  laplacian_out[comp] = hess_diag[comp][0];
5496  for (unsigned int d = 1; d < dim; ++d)
5497  laplacian_out[comp] += hess_diag[comp][d];
5498  }
5499  return laplacian_out;
5500 }

5561 template <int dim,
5562  int n_components_,
5563  typename Number,
5564  bool is_face,
5565  typename VectorizedArrayType>
5566 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE void
5567 FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
5568  submit_gradient(
5569  const Tensor<1, n_components_, Tensor<1, dim, VectorizedArrayType>> grad_in,
5570  const unsigned int q_point)
5571 {
5572  Assert(this->cell != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int, ExcNotInitialized());
5573  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
5574  Assert(this->J_value != nullptr,
5575  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
5576  "update_gradients"));
5577  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
5578  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
5579  "update_gradients"));
5580 # ifdef DEBUG
5581  this->gradients_quad_submitted = true;
5582 # endif
5583 
5584  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
5585  if (!is_face && this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
5586  {
5587  const VectorizedArrayType JxW =
5588  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point];
5589  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5590  {
5591  const VectorizedArrayType factor = this->jacobian[0][d][d] * JxW;
5592  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5593  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] =
5594  grad_in[comp][d] * factor;
5595  }
5596  }
5597  else
5598  {
5599  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> jac =
5600  this->cell_type > internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
5601  this->jacobian[q_point] :
5602  this->jacobian[0];
5603  const VectorizedArrayType JxW =
5604  this->cell_type > internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
5605  this->J_value[q_point] :
5606  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point];
5607  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; ++comp)
5608  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5609  {
5610  VectorizedArrayType new_val = jac[0][d] * grad_in[comp][0];
5611  for (unsigned int e = 1; e < dim; ++e)
5612  new_val += (jac[e][d] * grad_in[comp][e]);
5613  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] = new_val * JxW;
5614  }
5615  }
5616 }

5620 template <int dim,
5621  int n_components_,
5622  typename Number,
5623  bool is_face,
5624  typename VectorizedArrayType>
5625 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE void
5626 FEEvaluationBase<dim, n_components_, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
5627  submit_normal_derivative(
5628  const Tensor<1, n_components_, VectorizedArrayType> grad_in,
5629  const unsigned int q_point)
5630 {
5631  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
5632  Assert(this->normal_x_jacobian != nullptr,
5633  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
5634  "update_gradients"));
5635 # ifdef DEBUG
5636  this->gradients_quad_submitted = true;
5637 # endif
5638 
5639  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
5640  if (this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
5641  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5642  {
5643  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim - 1; ++d)
5644  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] =
5645  VectorizedArrayType();
5646  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + dim - 1) * nqp + q_point] =
5647  grad_in[comp] *
5648  (this->normal_x_jacobian[0][dim - 1] * this->J_value[0] *
5649  this->quadrature_weights[q_point]);
5650  }
5651  else
5652  {
5653  const unsigned int index =
5654  this->cell_type <= internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ? 0 : q_point;
5655  const Tensor<1, dim, VectorizedArrayType> jac =
5656  this->normal_x_jacobian[index];
5657  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < n_components; comp++)
5658  {
5659  VectorizedArrayType factor = grad_in[comp] * this->J_value[index];
5660  if (this->cell_type <= internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine)
5661  factor = factor * this->quadrature_weights[q_point];
5662  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5663  gradients_quad[(comp * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] = factor * jac[d];
5664  }
5665  }
5666 }

5679  Assert(this->cell != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int, ExcNotInitialized());

5921 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
5922 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE Tensor<1, dim, VectorizedArrayType>
5923  FEEvaluationAccess<dim, 1, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::get_gradient(
5924  const unsigned int q_point) const
5925 {
5926  // could use the base class gradient, but that involves too many expensive
5927  // initialization operations on tensors
5928 
5929 # ifdef DEBUG
5930  Assert(this->gradients_quad_initialized == true,
5931  internal::ExcAccessToUninitializedField());
5932 # endif
5933  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
5934 
5935  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
5936  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
5937  "update_gradients"));
5938 
5939  Tensor<1, dim, VectorizedArrayType> grad_out;
5940 
5941  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
5942  if (!is_face && this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
5943  {
5944  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5945  grad_out[d] =
5946  this->gradients_quad[d * nqp + q_point] * this->jacobian[0][d][d];
5947  }
5948  // cell with general/affine Jacobian
5949  else
5950  {
5951  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
5952  this->jacobian[this->cell_type > internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
5953  q_point :
5954  0];
5955  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
5956  {
5957  grad_out[d] = jac[d][0] * this->gradients_quad[q_point];
5958  for (unsigned int e = 1; e < dim; ++e)
5959  grad_out[d] += jac[d][e] * this->gradients_quad[e * nqp + q_point];
5960  }
5961  }
5962  return grad_out;
5963 }

6087  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6088  this->gradients_quad[d * nqp + q_point] =
6089  (grad_in[d] * this->jacobian[0][d][d] * JxW);
6090  }
6091  // general/affine cell type
6092  else
6093  {
6094  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
6095  this->cell_type > internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
6096  this->jacobian[q_point] :
6097  this->jacobian[0];
6098  const VectorizedArrayType JxW =
6099  this->cell_type > internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine ?
6100  this->J_value[q_point] :
6101  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point];
6102  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6103  {
6104  VectorizedArrayType new_val = jac[0][d] * grad_in[0];
6105  for (unsigned int e = 1; e < dim; ++e)
6106  new_val += jac[e][d] * grad_in[e];
6107  this->gradients_quad[d * nqp + q_point] = new_val * JxW;
6108  }
6109  }
6110 }

6209 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
6210 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE VectorizedArrayType
6211  FEEvaluationAccess<dim, dim, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
6212  get_divergence(const unsigned int q_point) const
6213 {
6214 # ifdef DEBUG
6215  Assert(this->gradients_quad_initialized == true,
6216  internal::ExcAccessToUninitializedField());
6217 # endif
6218  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
6219  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
6220  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
6221  "update_gradients"));
6222 
6223  VectorizedArrayType divergence;
6224  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
6225 
6226  // Cartesian cell
6227  if (!is_face && this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
6228  {
6229  divergence = this->gradients_quad[q_point] * this->jacobian[0][0][0];
6230  for (unsigned int d = 1; d < dim; ++d)
6231  divergence += this->gradients_quad[(dim * d + d) * nqp + q_point] *
6232  this->jacobian[0][d][d];
6233  }
6234  // cell with general/constant Jacobian
6235  else
6236  {
6237  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
6238  this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?
6239  this->jacobian[q_point] :
6240  this->jacobian[0];
6241  divergence = jac[0][0] * this->gradients_quad[q_point];
6242  for (unsigned int e = 1; e < dim; ++e)
6243  divergence += jac[0][e] * this->gradients_quad[e * nqp + q_point];
6244  for (unsigned int d = 1; d < dim; ++d)
6245  for (unsigned int e = 0; e < dim; ++e)
6246  divergence +=
6247  jac[d][e] * this->gradients_quad[(d * dim + e) * nqp + q_point];
6248  }
6249  return divergence;
6250 }

6254 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
6255 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE SymmetricTensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType>
6256  FEEvaluationAccess<dim, dim, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
6257  get_symmetric_gradient(const unsigned int q_point) const
6258 {
6259  // copy from generic function into dim-specialization function
6260  const auto grad = get_gradient(q_point);
6261  VectorizedArrayType symmetrized[(dim * dim + dim) / 2];
6262  VectorizedArrayType half = Number(0.5);
6263  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6264  symmetrized[d] = grad[d][d];
6265  switch (dim)
6266  {
6267  case 1:
6268  break;
6269  case 2:
6270  symmetrized[2] = grad[0][1] + grad[1][0];
6271  symmetrized[2] *= half;
6272  break;
6273  case 3:
6274  symmetrized[3] = grad[0][1] + grad[1][0];
6275  symmetrized[3] *= half;
6276  symmetrized[4] = grad[0][2] + grad[2][0];
6277  symmetrized[4] *= half;
6278  symmetrized[5] = grad[1][2] + grad[2][1];
6279  symmetrized[5] *= half;
6280  break;
6281  default:
6282  Assert(false, ExcNotImplemented());
6283  }
6284  return SymmetricTensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType>(symmetrized);
6285 }

6289 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
6290 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE
6291  Tensor<1, (dim == 2 ? 1 : dim), VectorizedArrayType>
6292  FEEvaluationAccess<dim, dim, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::get_curl(
6293  const unsigned int q_point) const
6294 {
6295  // copy from generic function into dim-specialization function
6296  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> grad = get_gradient(q_point);
6297  Tensor<1, (dim == 2 ? 1 : dim), VectorizedArrayType> curl;
6298  switch (dim)
6299  {
6300  case 1:
6301  Assert(false,
6302  ExcMessage(
6303  "Computing the curl in 1d is not a useful operation"));
6304  break;
6305  case 2:
6306  curl[0] = grad[1][0] - grad[0][1];
6307  break;
6308  case 3:
6309  curl[0] = grad[2][1] - grad[1][2];
6310  curl[1] = grad[0][2] - grad[2][0];
6311  curl[2] = grad[1][0] - grad[0][1];
6312  break;
6313  default:
6314  Assert(false, ExcNotImplemented());
6315  }
6316  return curl;
6317 }

6369 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
6370 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE void
6371 FEEvaluationAccess<dim, dim, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
6372  submit_divergence(const VectorizedArrayType div_in,
6373  const unsigned int q_point)
6374 {
6375  Assert(this->cell != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int, ExcNotInitialized());
6376  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
6377  Assert(this->J_value != nullptr,
6378  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
6379  "update_gradients"));
6380  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
6381  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
6382  "update_gradients"));
6383 # ifdef DEBUG
6384  this->gradients_quad_submitted = true;
6385 # endif
6386 
6387  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
6388  if (!is_face && this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
6389  {
6390  const VectorizedArrayType fac =
6391  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point] * div_in;
6392  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6393  {
6394  this->gradients_quad[(d * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] =
6395  (fac * this->jacobian[0][d][d]);
6396  for (unsigned int e = d + 1; e < dim; ++e)
6397  {
6398  this->gradients_quad[(d * dim + e) * nqp + q_point] =
6399  VectorizedArrayType();
6400  this->gradients_quad[(e * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] =
6401  VectorizedArrayType();
6402  }
6403  }
6404  }
6405  else
6406  {
6407  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
6408  this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?
6409  this->jacobian[q_point] :
6410  this->jacobian[0];
6411  const VectorizedArrayType fac =
6412  (this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?
6413  this->J_value[q_point] :
6414  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point]) *
6415  div_in;
6416  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6417  {
6418  for (unsigned int e = 0; e < dim; ++e)
6419  this->gradients_quad[(d * dim + e) * nqp + q_point] =
6420  jac[d][e] * fac;
6421  }
6422  }
6423 }

6427 template <int dim, typename Number, bool is_face, typename VectorizedArrayType>
6428 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE void
6429 FEEvaluationAccess<dim, dim, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::
6430  submit_symmetric_gradient(
6431  const SymmetricTensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> sym_grad,
6432  const unsigned int q_point)
6433 {
6434  // could have used base class operator, but that involves some overhead
6435  // which is inefficient. it is nice to have the symmetric tensor because
6436  // that saves some operations
6437  Assert(this->cell != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int, ExcNotInitialized());
6438  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
6439  Assert(this->J_value != nullptr,
6440  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
6441  "update_gradients"));
6442  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr,
6443  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
6444  "update_gradients"));
6445 # ifdef DEBUG
6446  this->gradients_quad_submitted = true;
6447 # endif
6448 
6449  const std::size_t nqp = this->n_quadrature_points;
6450  if (!is_face && this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
6451  {
6452  const VectorizedArrayType JxW =
6453  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point];
6454  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6455  this->gradients_quad[(d * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] =
6456  (sym_grad.access_raw_entry(d) * JxW * this->jacobian[0][d][d]);
6457  for (unsigned int e = 0, counter = dim; e < dim; ++e)
6458  for (unsigned int d = e + 1; d < dim; ++d, ++counter)
6459  {
6460  const VectorizedArrayType value =
6461  sym_grad.access_raw_entry(counter) * JxW;
6462  this->gradients_quad[(e * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] =
6463  value * this->jacobian[0][d][d];
6464  this->gradients_quad[(d * dim + e) * nqp + q_point] =
6465  value * this->jacobian[0][e][e];
6466  }
6467  }
6468  // general/affine cell type
6469  else
6470  {
6471  const VectorizedArrayType JxW =
6472  this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?
6473  this->J_value[q_point] :
6474  this->J_value[0] * this->quadrature_weights[q_point];
6475  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac =
6476  this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?
6477  this->jacobian[q_point] :
6478  this->jacobian[0];
6479  VectorizedArrayType weighted[dim][dim];
6480  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < dim; ++i)
6481  weighted[i][i] = sym_grad.access_raw_entry(i) * JxW;
6482  for (unsigned int i = 0, counter = dim; i < dim; ++i)
6483  for (unsigned int j = i + 1; j < dim; ++j, ++counter)
6484  {
6485  const VectorizedArrayType value =
6486  sym_grad.access_raw_entry(counter) * JxW;
6487  weighted[i][j] = value;
6488  weighted[j][i] = value;
6489  }
6490  for (unsigned int comp = 0; comp < dim; ++comp)
6491  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
6492  {
6493  VectorizedArrayType new_val = jac[0][d] * weighted[comp][0];
6494  for (unsigned int e = 1; e < dim; ++e)
6495  new_val += jac[e][d] * weighted[comp][e];
6496  this->gradients_quad[(comp * dim + d) * nqp + q_point] = new_val;
6497  }
6498  }
6499 }

6504 inline DEAL_II_ALWAYS_INLINE void

6506  const Tensor<1, dim == 2 ? 1 : dim, VectorizedArrayType> curl,

6510  switch (dim)

6529  default:

6532  submit_gradient(grad, q_point);
6533 }

6729 {

6731  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);

6775 FEEvaluationAccess<1, 1, Number, is_face, VectorizedArrayType>::submit_gradient(
6776  const VectorizedArrayType grad_in,
6777  const unsigned int q_point)
6778 {
6779  Assert(this->cell != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int, ExcNotInitialized());
6780  AssertIndexRange(q_point, this->n_quadrature_points);
6781 # ifdef DEBUG
6782  this->gradients_quad_submitted = true;

6786  this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?

6788  this->jacobian[0];

6790  this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::general ?

6793

7052 template <int dim,
7053  int fe_degree,
7054  int n_q_points_1d,
7055  int n_components_,
7056  typename Number,
7057  typename VectorizedArrayType>
7058 inline void
7059 FEEvaluation<dim,
7060  fe_degree,
7061  n_q_points_1d,
7062  n_components_,
7063  Number,
7064  VectorizedArrayType>::
7065  check_template_arguments(const unsigned int dof_no,
7066  const unsigned int first_selected_component)
7067 {
7068  (void)dof_no;
7069  (void)first_selected_component;
7070 
7071 # ifdef DEBUG
7072  // print error message when the dimensions do not match. Propose a possible
7073  // fix
7074  if ((static_cast<unsigned int>(fe_degree) != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int &&
7075  static_cast<unsigned int>(fe_degree) !=
7076  this->data->data.front().fe_degree) ||
7077  n_q_points != this->n_quadrature_points)
7078  {
7079  std::string message =
7080  "-------------------------------------------------------\n";
7081  message += "Illegal arguments in constructor/wrong template arguments!\n";
7082  message += " Called --> FEEvaluation<dim,";
7083  message += Utilities::int_to_string(fe_degree) + ",";
7084  message += Utilities::int_to_string(n_q_points_1d);
7085  message += "," + Utilities::int_to_string(n_components);
7086  message += ",Number>(data";
7087  if (first_selected_component != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
7088  {
7089  message += ", " + Utilities::int_to_string(dof_no) + ", ";
7090  message += Utilities::int_to_string(this->quad_no) + ", ";
7091  message += Utilities::int_to_string(first_selected_component);
7092  }
7093  message += ")\n";
7094 
7095  // check whether some other vector component has the correct number of
7096  // points
7097  unsigned int proposed_dof_comp = numbers::invalid_unsigned_int,
7098  proposed_fe_comp = numbers::invalid_unsigned_int,
7099  proposed_quad_comp = numbers::invalid_unsigned_int;
7100  if (dof_no != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
7101  {
7102  if (static_cast<unsigned int>(fe_degree) ==
7103  this->data->data.front().fe_degree)
7104  {
7105  proposed_dof_comp = dof_no;
7106  proposed_fe_comp = first_selected_component;
7107  }
7108  else
7109  for (unsigned int no = 0; no < this->matrix_info->n_components();
7110  ++no)
7111  for (unsigned int nf = 0;
7112  nf < this->matrix_info->n_base_elements(no);
7113  ++nf)
7114  if (this->matrix_info
7115  ->get_shape_info(no, 0, nf, this->active_fe_index, 0)
7116  .data.front()
7117  .fe_degree == static_cast<unsigned int>(fe_degree))
7118  {
7119  proposed_dof_comp = no;
7120  proposed_fe_comp = nf;
7121  break;
7122  }
7123  if (n_q_points ==
7124  this->mapping_data->descriptor[this->active_quad_index]
7125  .n_q_points)
7126  proposed_quad_comp = this->quad_no;
7127  else
7128  for (unsigned int no = 0;
7129  no < this->matrix_info->get_mapping_info().cell_data.size();
7130  ++no)
7131  if (this->matrix_info->get_mapping_info()
7132  .cell_data[no]
7133  .descriptor[this->active_quad_index]
7134  .n_q_points == n_q_points)
7135  {
7136  proposed_quad_comp = no;
7137  break;
7138  }
7139  }
7140  if (proposed_dof_comp != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int &&
7141  proposed_quad_comp != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
7142  {
7143  if (proposed_dof_comp != first_selected_component)
7144  message += "Wrong vector component selection:\n";
7145  else
7146  message += "Wrong quadrature formula selection:\n";
7147  message += " Did you mean FEEvaluation<dim,";
7148  message += Utilities::int_to_string(fe_degree) + ",";
7149  message += Utilities::int_to_string(n_q_points_1d);
7150  message += "," + Utilities::int_to_string(n_components);
7151  message += ",Number>(data";
7152  if (dof_no != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
7153  {
7154  message +=
7155  ", " + Utilities::int_to_string(proposed_dof_comp) + ", ";
7156  message += Utilities::int_to_string(proposed_quad_comp) + ", ";
7157  message += Utilities::int_to_string(proposed_fe_comp);
7158  }
7159  message += ")?\n";
7160  std::string correct_pos;
7161  if (proposed_dof_comp != dof_no)
7162  correct_pos = " ^ ";
7163  else
7164  correct_pos = " ";
7165  if (proposed_quad_comp != this->quad_no)
7166  correct_pos += " ^ ";
7167  else
7168  correct_pos += " ";
7169  if (proposed_fe_comp != first_selected_component)
7170  correct_pos += " ^\n";
7171  else
7172  correct_pos += " \n";
7173  message += " " +
7174  correct_pos;
7175  }
7176  // ok, did not find the numbers specified by the template arguments in
7177  // the given list. Suggest correct template arguments
7178  const unsigned int proposed_n_q_points_1d = static_cast<unsigned int>(
7179  std::pow(1.001 * this->n_quadrature_points, 1. / dim));
7180  message += "Wrong template arguments:\n";
7181  message += " Did you mean FEEvaluation<dim,";
7182  message +=
7183  Utilities::int_to_string(this->data->data.front().fe_degree) + ",";
7184  message += Utilities::int_to_string(proposed_n_q_points_1d);
7185  message += "," + Utilities::int_to_string(n_components);
7186  message += ",Number>(data";
7187  if (dof_no != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
7188  {
7189  message += ", " + Utilities::int_to_string(dof_no) + ", ";
7190  message += Utilities::int_to_string(this->quad_no);
7191  message += ", " + Utilities::int_to_string(first_selected_component);
7192  }
7193  message += ")?\n";
7194  std::string correct_pos;
7195  if (this->data->data.front().fe_degree !=
7196  static_cast<unsigned int>(fe_degree))
7197  correct_pos = " ^";
7198  else
7199  correct_pos = " ";
7200  if (proposed_n_q_points_1d != n_q_points_1d)
7201  correct_pos += " ^\n";
7202  else
7203  correct_pos += " \n";
7204  message += " " + correct_pos;
7205 
7206  Assert(static_cast<unsigned int>(fe_degree) ==
7207  this->data->data.front().fe_degree &&
7208  n_q_points == this->n_quadrature_points,
7209  ExcMessage(message));
7210  }
7211  if (dof_no != numbers::invalid_unsigned_int)
7212  AssertDimension(
7213  n_q_points,
7214  this->mapping_data->descriptor[this->active_quad_index].n_q_points);
7215 # endif
7216 }

7320 template <int dim,
7321  int fe_degree,
7322  int n_q_points_1d,
7323  int n_components_,
7324  typename Number,
7325  typename VectorizedArrayType>
7326 inline Point<dim, VectorizedArrayType>
7327 FEEvaluation<dim,
7328  fe_degree,
7329  n_q_points_1d,
7330  n_components_,
7331  Number,
7332  VectorizedArrayType>::quadrature_point(const unsigned int q) const
7333 {
7334  if (this->matrix_info == nullptr)
7335  {
7336  Assert((this->mapped_geometry->get_fe_values().get_update_flags() |
7337  update_quadrature_points),
7338  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
7339  "update_quadrature_points"));
7340  }
7341  else
7342  {
7343  Assert(this->mapping_data->quadrature_point_offsets.empty() == false,
7344  internal::ExcMatrixFreeAccessToUninitializedMappingField(
7345  "update_quadrature_points"));
7346  }
7347 
7348  AssertIndexRange(q, n_q_points);
7349 
7350  const Point<dim, VectorizedArrayType> *quadrature_points =
7351  &this->mapping_data->quadrature_points
7352  [this->mapping_data->quadrature_point_offsets[this->cell]];
7353 
7354  // Cartesian/affine mesh: only first vertex of cell is stored, we must
7355  // compute it through the Jacobian (which is stored in non-inverted and
7356  // non-transposed form as index '1' in the jacobian field)
7357  if (this->cell_type <= internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::affine)
7358  {
7359  Assert(this->jacobian != nullptr, ExcNotInitialized());
7360  Point<dim, VectorizedArrayType> point = quadrature_points[0];
7361 
7362  const Tensor<2, dim, VectorizedArrayType> &jac = this->jacobian[1];
7363  if (this->cell_type == internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::cartesian)
7364  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
7365  point[d] += jac[d][d] * static_cast<Number>(
7366  this->descriptor->quadrature.point(q)[d]);
7367  else
7368  for (unsigned int d = 0; d < dim; ++d)
7369  for (unsigned int e = 0; e < dim; ++e)
7370  point[d] += jac[d][e] * static_cast<Number>(
7371  this->descriptor->quadrature.point(q)[e]);
7372  return point;
7373  }
7374  else
7375  return quadrature_points[q];
7376 }

7546  template <typename Number,
7547  typename VectorizedArrayType,
7548  typename VectorType,
7549  typename T,
7550  typename std::enable_if<
7551  internal::has_begin<VectorType>::value &&
7552  std::is_same<decltype(std::declval<VectorType>().begin()),
7553  Number *>::value,
7554  VectorType>::type * = nullptr>
7555  bool
7556  try_gather_evaluate_inplace(
7557  T phi,
7558  const VectorType & input_vector,
7559  const unsigned int cell,
7560  const unsigned int active_fe_index,
7561  const unsigned int first_selected_component,
7562  const internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo *dof_info,
7563  const EvaluationFlags::EvaluationFlags evaluation_flag)
7564  {
7565  // If the index storage is interleaved and contiguous and the vector storage
7566  // has the correct alignment, we can directly pass the pointer into the
7567  // vector to the evaluate() call, without reading the vector entries into a
7568  // separate data field. This saves some operations.
7569  if (std::is_same<typename VectorType::value_type, Number>::value &&
7570  dof_info->index_storage_variants
7571  [internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell][cell] ==
7572  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::IndexStorageVariants::
7573  interleaved_contiguous &&
7574  reinterpret_cast<std::size_t>(
7575  input_vector.begin() +
7576  dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous
7577  [internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell]
7578  [cell * VectorizedArrayType::size()]) %
7579  sizeof(VectorizedArrayType) ==
7580  0)
7581  {
7582  const VectorizedArrayType *vec_values =
7583  reinterpret_cast<const VectorizedArrayType *>(
7584  input_vector.begin() +
7585  dof_info->dof_indices_contiguous
7586  [internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_cell]
7587  [cell * VectorizedArrayType::size()] +
7588  dof_info->component_dof_indices_offset[active_fe_index]
7589  [first_selected_component] *
7590  VectorizedArrayType::size());
7591 
7592  phi->evaluate(vec_values, evaluation_flag);
7593 
7594  return true;
7595  }
7596 
7597  return false;
7598  }

7696  vec_values,
7697  values_quad,
7698  gradients_quad,
7699  scratch_data,
7700  true);

8054 template <int dim,
8055  int fe_degree,
8056  int n_q_points_1d,
8057  int n_components_,
8058  typename Number,
8059  typename VectorizedArrayType>
8060 inline void
8061 FEFaceEvaluation<dim,
8062  fe_degree,
8063  n_q_points_1d,
8064  n_components_,
8065  Number,
8066  VectorizedArrayType>::reinit(const unsigned int face_index)
8067 {
8068  Assert(this->mapped_geometry == nullptr,
8069  ExcMessage("FEEvaluation was initialized without a matrix-free object."
8070  " Integer indexing is not possible"));
8071  if (this->mapped_geometry != nullptr)
8072  return;
8073 
8074  this->cell = face_index;
8075  this->dof_access_index =
8076  this->is_interior_face ?
8077  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_face_interior :
8078  internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::DoFInfo::dof_access_face_exterior;
8079  Assert(this->mapping_data != nullptr, ExcNotInitialized());
8080  const internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::FaceToCellTopology<
8081  VectorizedArrayType::size()> &faces =
8082  this->matrix_info->get_face_info(face_index);
8083  if (face_index >=
8084  this->matrix_info->get_task_info().face_partition_data.back() &&
8085  face_index <
8086  this->matrix_info->get_task_info().boundary_partition_data.back())
8087  Assert(this->is_interior_face,
8088  ExcMessage(
8089  "Boundary faces do not have a neighbor. When looping over "
8090  "boundary faces use FEFaceEvaluation with the parameter "
8091  "is_interior_face set to true. "));
8092 
8093  this->face_no =
8094  (this->is_interior_face ? faces.interior_face_no : faces.exterior_face_no);
8095  this->subface_index = this->is_interior_face == true ?
8096  GeometryInfo<dim>::max_children_per_cell :
8097  faces.subface_index;
8098 
8099  // First check if interior or exterior cell has non-standard orientation
8100  // (i.e. the third bit is one or not). Then set zero if this cell has
8101  // standard-orientation else copy the first three bits
8102  // (which is equivalent to modulo 8). See also the documentation of
8103  // internal::MatrixFreeFunctions::FaceToCellTopology::face_orientation.
8104  this->face_orientation =
8105  (this->is_interior_face == (faces.face_orientation >= 8)) ?
8106  (faces.face_orientation % 8) :
8107  0;
8108 
8109  this->cell_type = this->matrix_info->get_mapping_info().face_type[face_index];
8110  const unsigned int offsets =
8111  this->mapping_data->data_index_offsets[face_index];
8112  this->J_value = &this->mapping_data->JxW_values[offsets];
8113  this->normal_vectors = &this->mapping_data->normal_vectors[offsets];
8114  this->jacobian =
8115  &this->mapping_data->jacobians[!this->is_interior_face][offsets];
8116  this->normal_x_jacobian =
8117  &this->mapping_data
8118  ->normals_times_jacobians[!this->is_interior_face][offsets];
8119 
8120 # ifdef DEBUG
8121  this->dof_values_initialized = false;
8122  this->values_quad_initialized = false;
8123  this->gradients_quad_initialized = false;
8124  this->hessians_quad_initialized = false;
8125 # endif
8126 }
